          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Attendance is first priority of college which is good",
          "name": "Aditya Birare",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college have a very big capmus,the college is the one the best college in the city, the college have very big library for the study, the college have a near of highways so the transportation ia easy for college student",
          "name": "Sahil Shirsath",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college have a two big canteens one is inside the building, one is the common canteen for all",
