          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Good for education and the extra Curiucular activities is good",
          "name": "Sahil Shirsath",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The faculty of our college very supportive. They always clear the doubts of each an every one",
          "name": "Sofiyan",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus is clean,it maintains hygiene , because of it no one can fall ill",
